patthana23.4:1.1_0: Nakusalaṁ nasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā akusalo saṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …. (Akusalāneva tīṇi.
patthana23.4:2.1_0: Nakusalaṁ naasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca abyākato asaṅkiliṭṭhaasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha,
patthana23.4:2.1_1: adhipatiyā cha …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate pañca.
patthana23.4:3.1_0: Nakusalaṁ naasaṅkiliṭṭhaasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā kusalo asaṅkiliṭṭhaasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha,
patthana23.4:3.1_1: ārammaṇe cha …pe… āsevane tīṇi …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
